---
title: Steak and Brussels Sprout Stir-Fry with Carrot, Ginger, and Jasmine Rice
description: Brussels sprouts and stir-fry may sound like an unlikely pair, but trust us, it works. The addition of this cruciferous veggie adds a seasonal flair to the dish—not to mention a hefty dose of iron and Vitamins A and C. Feel free to add as much or as little jalapeño as you like. After all, you’re the chef!
